{"tid":1929806,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】猶太教領袖呼籲教徒避免親吻耶路撒冷「哭牆」","createTime":"2020-03-17T07:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T07:57:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ead62a61394c0e9e194bc1b2448e70c86e66296","tid":1929806,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514839-20200316.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514839-20200316.htm&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8FyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=77410a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514839-20200316.htm&h=75482c8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514839-20200316.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1514839_1_L_20200316205052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1514839_1_L_20200316205052.jpg&h=c4b37307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名猶太教首席領袖呼籲猶太教徒，因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，應避免親吻耶路撒冷「哭牆」的石頭。<br />\n<br />\n這名領袖在一個猶太教網站又說，宗教部門已採取必要措施，減低病毒傳播。<br />\n<br />\n「哭牆」是猶太教昔日聖殿的唯一遺蹟，被猶太教徒視為至高聖地，牆身的石縫塞滿了祈禱紙條，親吻石牆不是禮節性要求，但是一些虔誠的猶太人堅持這樣做，相信可以表明對上帝的敬意。<br />\n<br />\n以色列至今錄得255宗確診武漢肺炎個案，其中近40宗來自西岸。"},{"pid":"d4a77e5b0b17267a45b301d7d80a85c4b4bff6a7","tid":1929806,"uid":314136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"即刻見上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4f665445b2d263591408e6c79112d270a5ad7d","tid":1929806,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"受到聖靈感召"},{"pid":"0fe6ae1a52d8c2008e2a94703028e28fd1fa74b4","tid":1929806,"uid":61357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"間接kiss牆<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gi